title: Mrs Luisa Cescutti-Butler
text: I bought a pair of tennis and running shoes from the sale. The shoes arrived promptly. I have tried the tennis shoes and am satisfied with their quality and appearance. have not yet had a chance to use the running shoes. Overall I am satisfied with my online Tennisnuts shopping experience
